# ShopSmart E-Commerce

Spring Boot 3.3 + Rust sidecar e-commerce learning project.

## Stack & Run

- Java 17, Maven, package `com.shopsmart`
- Spring Web MVC + JPA + Security + Thymeleaf + Flyway (V1–V6)
- Rust Axum sidecar: `rust-service/` on **:8081**
- **Main app:** `mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run` → **http://localhost:8080** (not port 80)
- **Rust:** `cd rust-service && cargo run` → http://localhost:8081
- Test: `mvnw.cmd test` (51 tests)

## Architecture

| Layer | Location |
|-------|----------|
| REST + UI | `controller/*`, `templates/*.html` |
| Rust analytics | `rust-service/` (proxies Spring via Basic auth) |
| Persistence | `repository/`, `model/`, `db/migration/` |
| Security | `SecurityConfig` — form login + HTTP Basic, ADMIN/USER |

Business logic mostly in controllers. CSRF disabled.

